articles.author: Ellise Shafer
articles.title: Taylor Swift Plays ‘The Tortured Poets Department’ Songs Live for the First Time at Paris Eras Tour Show - Variety
articles.description: Taylor Swift debuted songs from new album 'The Tortured Poets Department' at the European opener of her Eras Tour in Paris.
articles.content:
